responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "754067934C0917D4EFF068A0E241B011", "Once, we belonged here. It may not haunt your dreams nor mine, but we were torn away from this place. And while we respect the Sandsquall, the Zephyr Wind has returned. We are prepared to reclaim our history from the desert\'s crystalline claws and we use them to make our people stronger. Let us never abandon this place again.")
